## Schema

Each row is one MLP. Columns:

| Column | Type | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `mlp_id` | `int32` | 0-based row index |
| `mlp_name` | `string` | Deterministic faker-derived slug, e.g. `"danielle-johnson"` |
| `mlp_seed` | `int64` | Per-MLP grader-supplied seed |
| `weights` | `float32[depth][width][width]` | Layer weight matrices |
| `all_layer_means` | `float32[depth][width]` | Ground-truth per-layer means |
| `final_means` | `float32[width]` | Ground-truth final-layer means |
| `avg_variance` | `float64` | Across-layer mean variance |
| `sampling_budget_breakdown` | `string` (JSON) | FLOP accounting from the bake |

